Using Bootstrap, you are required to create a fully responsive design of WhatsApp. You are supposed to get the basic layout idea
from the mobile application and the web application. You are free to change the theme colors, icons, message features etc.
You submission should have following pages -
1) A main page displaying all the chat messages.
2) A chat view page containing messages with an individual or a group
3) A view to change the profile picture.
Page should be fully responsive
